      "rationale": "Per ASME V&V 40 Table 1, numerical solver error assessment is not required at MRL 2 when discretization error and SQA factors are both assessed and met. Scoped out by agreement with regulatory team."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Use error",
