      "rationale": "Use error assessment not required at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 1 for the current device class and decision context. Analyst training records and simulation SOPs maintained as administrative controls outside the formal credibility assessment."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
