    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are explicitly scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 1 requirements for MRL 2, Class II device context. Hemolysis index prediction error (12%) is within the pre-specified 15% tolerance. The assessment team concludes the CFD model has sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump in the CPB application. Regulatory submission package approved for filing.",
